      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patrick Farrell\t\tOct 9 10:34 AM\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n\n> In light of LU-3601 going away due to other changes, is there any plan to land a version of this patch, or is it expected to be abandoned?\n\nThe plan is for it to be reworked and resubmitted eventually. The may be some corner cases in HSM that could still benefit from this patch but other than that I do not see any LDLM uses that require it for correctness. (If you see one then please say so on Jira.) Have you tested this patch and found it beneficial to any workloads?",
